        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Motor Carriers Accountability Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires motor carriers that operate passenger services on standard coach buses with 50 or more seats to adopt contingency plans for excessive passenger delays.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
